Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Fullmetal Alchemist,0000,0000,0000,,Brotherhood
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Fullmetal Alchemist,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 30
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Fullmetal Alchemist,0000,0000,0000,,===============================================================
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,

Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.12,0:01:37.99,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So in the end, you became a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.93,0:01:43.37,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, it's far too early to teach you the art of flame alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:45.57,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Still, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.99,0:01:50.75,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You've only taught me the basics of alchemy so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:52.87,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:02:00.54,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who would sink to becoming a dog of the military is unworthy of being taught even the basics of alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:04.56,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemy should be used for the benefit of the masses. Isn't that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.86,0:02:13.30,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx99}Master, we're currently under threat from neighboring countries. We're in an urgent need to strengthen our forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:16.16,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemy is essential for protecting the people-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:18.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired of hearing that same excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.27,0:02:27.12,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't sit here and watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:31.91,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Someone as talented as you suffering crushing poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:34.17,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Please become a State Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:36.41,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, you'll be able to conduct other experiments-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:39.42,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I've already completed my experiments long in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:41.64,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,What did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:45.41,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The most powerful alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.41,0:02:48.82,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Though depending on how it's used, it could be the most deadly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:51.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I perfected it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:54.65,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,...and became satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:03:03.43,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemists are creatures who must continually strive toward the truth as long as they are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.86,0:03:08.20,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They die as soon as they stop the process of thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:12.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I had already died long in the past-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:14.04,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:18.25,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:19.17,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Master Hawkeye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:22.39,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Take care... of my daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:28.18,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Every detail of my experiment... is with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:42.37,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for having to rely on you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:44.04,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.04,0:03:45.79,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It's my duty as a former student.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:50.56,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hesitate to visit me at the military if anything happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:57.80,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you also going to judge me for becoming a soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:04:02.28,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,As everyone may say, there is a chance I'll end up dying like a piece of trash out on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:10.41,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,But even then, if it means I'll be able to protect this country, I don't mind at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:14.77,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry if I'm boring you. It's a childish dream of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:16.97,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.39,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's quite admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:23.65,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,A future where everyone will be able to live in happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:25.92,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Can I trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:30.77,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Can I entrust you with Father's dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:45.05,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:47.99,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.99,0:04:50.64,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine... It happens a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:52.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:54.39,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Assistant to the Führer President?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.49,0:04:56.60,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:01.98,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you had a rough time out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:04.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't shoot anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:06.32,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.70,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No... I couldn't bring myself to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:16.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:19.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm not prepared, I end up troubling others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:22.97,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:28.64,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Scar was the one who killed Winry's parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:35.29,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I had a horrible feeling in my gut at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:38.66,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,In my mind, the gun suddenly turned into something horrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:40.69,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And when I realized it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:47.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I think she despised Scar enough to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.19,0:05:50.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never seen her cry as much as she did after he left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:54.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:58.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't understand her feelings at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:06:01.91,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,You can only worry about something like that because you came back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:05.25,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,But you have to survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.87,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,...for the sake of the people important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:10.52,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,You have to protect her, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:14.39,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,You love Winry, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:19.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! I-I-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:21.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,S-She's just a childhood friend of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:23.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just like family!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:25.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,P-Protecting her is nothing out of the ordinary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:26.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:27.40,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:31.24,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like this was a burden on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:40.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever thought of it as a burden?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:46.33,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even have the right to complain about its weight anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:50.76,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I've taken the lives of many people in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:56.02,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm also the one who chose this path.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.78,0:06:58.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Are you referring to Ishbal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:04.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind if I ask you about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:11.03,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Let me hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:15.03,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,What did you wretches do in Ishbal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:20.53,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Ishbal was a rough place to live, full of rocks and sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:28.72,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,So it's only fitting that a strict religion and\Na tenacious race of people reside there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:36.05,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,But some people were unhappy\Nthat they were annexed to Amestris.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:38.48,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,And just then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:49.36,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Because of one bullet, the unhappiness evolved into anger and spread throughout Ishbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:59.47,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,The riot turned into a civil war and continued on for seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:05.79,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Then, one document decided everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:09.46,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Executive Order No. 3066.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:13.09,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,It began the Ishbal Extermination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:14.93,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Just that one sheet of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:34.36,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,It was a living hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:38.64,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,The air was choked with the stench of rotting corpses and gunpowder,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:41.80,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,and the sand was soaked with blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:54.84,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,An infantryman could fire at random, and if lucky, he might hit someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:57.14,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,But sniping is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:09:00.47,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,When you pull the trigger, someone dies for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:05.49,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,The two groups who were the most closely related in terms of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.49,0:09:06.87,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,...would be snipers...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:10.82,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,...and State Alchemists.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:17.95,Default,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Basque Gran, the Iron Blood Alchemist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:19.95,Default,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,Iron and Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:22.37,Default,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Weapons and Soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:27.54,Default,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,Who else would be more fitting to stand at the forefront?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:06.65,Default,Koma,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:08.25,Default,Koma,0000,0000,0000,,Ishbalan brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:11.60,Default,Koma,0000,0000,0000,,How... How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.33,0:10:15.05,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,Roy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:16.77,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,Roy Mustang!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:22.48,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,So you were here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:23.99,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:25.31,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,But man,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.59,0:10:27.68,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,your eyes look different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.59,0:10:32.31,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Same with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:34.63,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,We all have the eyes of murderers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:36.82,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:44.14,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we all talk about the future of this country at the military academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:45.08,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:47.83,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,A beautiful future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:50.38,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, a letter for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:52.33,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:55.06,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:55.84,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:57.96,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,My beautiful future!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:00.02,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,Her name's Gracia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:03.90,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,She's waiting for my return in Central!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:05.85,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,Alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:10.27,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,What if other guys hit on her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:15.19,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's no way Gracia would cheat on a handsome guy like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.84,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:19.55,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Hughes, let me warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:22.63,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,This happens a lot in both movies and novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:25.78,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who talks about his lover on a battlefield...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:26.89,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,...ends up dying right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:29.17,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:35.90,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,This is what keeps me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:41.48,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,This letter, and this letter only, lets me dream of tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:45.39,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,In this war that may never end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:49.01,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. There's no telling when this war will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:55.65,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many troops the country deploys, the desert just absorbs them like water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:11:59.97,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,We suffer, conquer, and what's left?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:02.40,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing but sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:06.98,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's far too big of an operation for it to merely be suppression.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:14.83,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Major Mustang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:17.34,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.91,0:12:19.39,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,How terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.86,0:12:20.84,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,This woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:23.56,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,...now also bears the eyes of murderers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:36.10,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:41.32,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Soldiers are supposed to protect the people. Why are we killing them instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:47.84,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemy is supposed to bring people happiness. Why is it being used for murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:52.70,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Because that's the State Alchemists' job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:57.45,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Why are soldiers killing the people?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:13:00.59,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Because that's what we were ordered to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:02.67,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.19,0:13:06.32,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling us to look at this horrible scene rationally?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:09.76,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... for example...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:15.45,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Girl, your face has the expression of "I'm doing this against my will".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.74,0:13:21.52,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Can you say for certain that there hasn't been a time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:27.27,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,...when you successfully sniped your enemy and felt good about your skill?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.65,0:13:28.93,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sniper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:31.15,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:35.96,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,From my point of view, it's you all who can't be understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:38.83,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,A battlefield is a place for murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:44.34,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Did you put on that uniform\Nwithout being prepared to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:49.09,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look away from death. Look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:53.85,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,When you kill, face them directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.35,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,And don't forget them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:59.19,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Your enemies will never forget you either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.14,0:14:04.38,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:06.64,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I need to head off to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:09.33,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:11.19,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.19,0:14:12.22,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Hughes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:14.70,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:18.17,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:21.42,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to die. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:24.21,Default,Hugh,0000,0000,0000,,Reasons are always simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:35.31,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Then what is the reason behind this war?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:37.81,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:41.96,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,...was a reason. A horrible reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.96,0:15:19.81,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,You created a philosopher's stone using our blood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:21.85,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do with that stone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:25.68,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,It went to the hands of Major Zolf J. Kimblee...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:28.40,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,...the Crimson Alchemist...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.02,0:15:33.33,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,The man with cold eyes...\Nwho has his long black hair tied back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:34.40,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:36.98,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:40.65,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,What else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.65,0:15:45.29,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The war situation changed with just one intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:50.55,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Such beautiful sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:55.17,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Such wondrous sounds ringing throughout my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:59.68,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,My spinal cord dances with sadness. My eardrum shivers with joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:07.19,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,This feeling can only be achieved here, where we lay so close to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:11.07,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful career!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:20.17,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,A beautiful sound!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.17,0:16:24.05,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! The philosopher's stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:32.47,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,It was only a matter of time before the extermination was complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:42.32,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,And then, the Ishbalan priest of highest rank, Roug Roa, stood before the Führer President to save his people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:44.48,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:50.19,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,So you want me to trade the lives of the tens of thousands of Ishbalans in exchange for your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:52.34,Default,Roug,0000,0000,0000,,Correct. I'm-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:53.49,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be conceited.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:59.93,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to say that your life is worth just as much as the lives of the ones who are left?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:02.87,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get ahead of yourself, human.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:07.46,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,A person's life is worth as much as anyone else's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:10.13,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,No more, no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:11.98,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I won't accept the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:13.45,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Nor will I call off the extermination.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:15.09,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:16.51,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,God will smite you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:18.47,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,"God"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:20.55,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,How strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:24.77,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,After all this, I've yet to be smote.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:30.52,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,How many more Ishbalans must I kill for that to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:32.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:38.53,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,God is only a figure created by humans;\Nthat's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:46.79,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to bring an iron hammer down on me,\Ndo it yourself without having to rely on God, human!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:55.55,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,And eventually, the war ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:59.44,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,and we were allowed to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:04.18,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we soldiers are nothing but trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:05.59,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:08.73,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,One human only has the power to do so much. {ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:12.51,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm going to protect... {ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.37,0:18:15.04,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,...even if it's just a handful of them... {ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:16.79,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,...the ones most important to me. {ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:21.23,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,A subordinate protects their subordinate, and so forth. {ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:25.16,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,That should be possible, even for us puny humans. {ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:48.60,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,So you decided to take this path,\Neven after what you experienced in Ishbal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:49.95,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:55.49,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,If this world is based on the concept of\Nequivalent exchange, as stated in alchemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:19:05.29,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,then we must carry corpses and cross the river of blood in exchange for the new generation to live in happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:11.61,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm appointing you as my assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:14.67,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to protect my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:18.13,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:22.89,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm leaving you in charge of defending my back,\Nit means you can shoot me from behind at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:27.25,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,If I ever stray from my path,\Nshoot me right away with those hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:29.93,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You have that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:32.10,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Will you follow me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.81,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:37.58,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish, I will follow you to the depths of Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:48.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But even if the Colonel becomes the Führer, it wouldn't change the militaristic element of this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:50.53,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:53.75,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Congress pretty much exists as the army's puppet right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:57.34,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Someone would need to change that and turn this country into a democracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:20:03.63,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,For this country to be reborn, all the faults that existed from the militaristic regime will have to be brushed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:04.59,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Faults?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:11.60,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx92}For example, the government may have to pass judgment on those who committed atrocities during the Ishbal Extermination.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:14.41,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.41,0:20:19.30,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,The heroes during the troubled times are nothing but mass murderers during times of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:22.18,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So the Colonel is reaching for the top while knowing about all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:24.60,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He's only on a path of self-destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:29.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The Homunculi are the ones who were pulling the strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:35.37,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the Homunculi were the ones who triggered it,\Nwe're the ones who committed the atrocities.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:39.17,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,We mustn't turn away from death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:42.36,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,We mustn't forget the ones we killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:43.26,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:48.18,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,...they'll never forget us, the ones who killed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:50.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:56.11,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have something to do before you start worrying about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.49,0:20:59.95,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Both you and Alphonse need to return to your bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:04.73,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure a lot of people are waiting for the day you reach your goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:08.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:11.96,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely get my body back. Together with Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:16.25,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for letting us stay, Dr. Nox.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:18.63,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Mister Armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:23.38,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Really, thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:27.02,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I have a name, you know. It's Alphonse Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:28.52,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Elric?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:31.47,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You remember Edward Elric, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.47,0:21:33.35,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,That small alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:35.31,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'm his younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.05,0:21:38.71,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my body due to certain circumstances, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:41.43,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,If you're that guy's younger brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.43,0:21:43.48,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,...does this mean you look just like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:44.24,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:48.01,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'm much taller than him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:51.83,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,My face isn't that stern, and I'm much stronger than him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:53.60,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not short-tempered, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:21:54.83,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a gentleman!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.27,0:21:58.71,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Alphonse!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.89,0:22:02.46,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you get your body back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:05.81,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I hope so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.42,0:23:40.48,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Marcoh, I've brought your meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.92,0:23:44.81,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's awfully quiet in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.05,0:23:48.59,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be you're crying again, reminiscing about Ishbal?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.02,0:24:00.90,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The White Devil has been released into the wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.90,0:24:04.04,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The new fight begins now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:06.34,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But the boy will not flinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.59,0:24:10.20,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He gets up and walks again, with hope as his landmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.82,0:24:15.18,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.18,0:24:19.93,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 31, The Promise Made For 520 Cenz.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.11,0:24:25.00,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The world which can only be understood by the ones who fought together is right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.00,0:24:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
